.alert.alert-info
  This is the complete list of demo users.
  No access permissions are applied here for the purposes of the demo (so you can see what is setup).
  Of course, in a real application, this resource view would be subject to access controls.

%table.table
  %thead
    %tr
      %th ID
      %th Username
      %th Description
      %th Company
      %th Group
      %th Roles

  %tbody
    - collection.each do |row|
      %tr
        %td.test_id= row.id
        %td= row.username
        %td= row.description
        %td= row.customer_name
        %td= row.group_name
        %td= row.role_names_list